name: There Is Alien In My Nose
description: There is an alien in my nose is a response to a text generator who develop by open artificial intelligence. It is a fun and interesting technology we can play and use. However artificial intelligent and generator texts it is not an easy technology to develop, and also it contains controversy in our society since it possibility destroy humanity or it will be useful for our humanity if we can control the lack and the dark side of artificial intelligence technology.
